Launched in 2010, Telkom Mobile grew immensely. Its growth is attributed to having 
emerged from Telkom,  which is an established fixed telecommunication network in South 
Africa. In 2013 Telkom launched 8ta . 8ta is now known as Telkom Mobile. Telkom Mobile 
is already in use in the business market while the Telkom Mobile brand is targeted at the 
