consumer market. Despite having managed to distinguish itself in data, with low price, high 
volume deals and access to Wi -Fi.  Telkom Mobile has a unique marketing approach in its 
market segmentation, with its brand structured to appeal to younger subscribers who tended  
to spend less. As the participants in this study comprised exclusively of youth from tertiary 
institutions, having “youth dominance” in the Telkom Mobile sample could not be tested. 
However, focusing on a particular target market and adding appropriate va lue, Telkom can 
