(2009: 70) argued that it is ten times more expensive to acquire a new customer than to retain 
an existing one. 
In addition, research by Keiningham et al. (2005: 174-178) revealed that customer retention 
is five times more cost effective than cust omer acquisition, while Apergis et al. (2008: 501) 
